  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p912777/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img height=\"300\" src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/11/15/193921e06f94ba1b915fbefd5942b965.jpg\" width=\"524\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tWhile &ldquo;Doctor Who&rdquo; will return in 2017 for a final season with Steven Moffat at the helm &mdash; Peter Capaldi returning as the Doctor, and Pearl Mackie playing his new assistant Bill &mdash; what happen after that remains a mystery.由编剧Steven Moffat编写的《神秘博士》最终季将在2017年回归，Peter Capaldi重回出演&ldquo;神秘博士&rdquo;，Pearl Mackie出演他的新助理Bill，接下来的剧情尚不清楚。</p>\n<p>\n\tWhat we know is that &ldquo;Broadchurch&rdquo; creator Chris Chibnall will be taking over as showrunner, leading &ldquo;Doctor Who&rdquo; into the future. But will he be doing it with an all new cast? A report from the UK&rsquo;s &ldquo;Mirror,&rdquo; admittedly not always the most trustworthy of outlets, claims the long-running BBC show may be looking to clean house and start fresh.美剧《小镇疑云》的创剧人Chris Chibnall将作为制片人接手本剧。但他将会在剧组大换血吗？英国《镜报》报道称，这部剧在收视方面并不是一直很稳定，声称，BBC Show可能会弃剧。</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;&ldquo;Doctor Who&rdquo; &mdash; which is returning for the annual&nbsp;Christmas special in December &mdash; isn&rsquo;t going anywhere. Perhaps this could also be the time for producers to finally give fans a Doctor that isn&rsquo;t a white male, too.《神秘博士》每年都是在12月份圣诞节时候回归。这也可能是剧组给粉丝们的最后一次非白人&ldquo;博士&rdquo;了。</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本双语文章的中文翻译系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p912777/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p912777\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style