  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-top-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; line-height: 1.8em; border-top-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>&nbsp;</span><img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201608/5928db29-27d0-4165-88e4-ae95a9ecb208.jpg\" /><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tMix<br />\n\tTo mix means to combine two or more things together, blending the components together. What is mixed? How are the components mixed? What is the reason?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They mixed everything together... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) mixing music at a club<br />\n\t2) mix ingredients for a recipe<br />\n\t3) mixing business with pleasure<br />\n\t4) mix in with the crowd<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThe interior designer added some sugar and cream in his drink. As he was mixing it altogether, he glanced at the club manager, who was still going through the sketches. Reaching over for his coffee, the club manager did not add any sugar nor cream is his coffee. The interior noted to himself that the club manager preferred black coffee. As he placed his black coffee back down on the desk surface, the manager concluded that all the sketches were good to go, and that he liked the concept design very much.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/169854932066/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p869660/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p869660\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p905050/\">史上最糟糕的学习方法，你中招了吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p749165/\">英语四级作文：10个你想不到的总结句式</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p828581/\